our kitchen and this recipe makes plenty - will store for up to a month in the fridge, or frozen in small batches for up to three months.","Top up with a little more oil after each use so the paste stays submerged; this helps to preserve it.","To make a smaller quantity, halve the ingredients and cook for 25 minutes in step 3."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h","1 total recipe"]}